'''Abderaḥman Bugarmuḥ''', d amseḍru n isura n tilizri d sinima azwaw. Ilul ass n 25 di [[Fuṛaṛ]] aseggas 1936 deg [[Aqbu|uqbu]], tamnaṭ n [[Bgayet]], immut ass n 3 [[Fuṛaṛ]] asegwas [[2013]] di ldzayer.

D netta i d-isufɣen asaru ameqqran amezwaru s [[Tamaziɣt|tmaziɣt]] / [[tazwawt]] deg aseggas 1996. Isem-is '''[[Tawrirt yettwattun]]''' (La colline oubliée), i yellan d adlis umyaru [[Lmulud Mɛemri|Mulud At Mɛammar]].


== Tameddurt-is ==

Ilul deg uzellagen ass n 25 [[Fuṛaṛ]] asegwas 1936, yella d mmis n uselmad n-uɣarbaz afṛansi aqbuṛ, yemma-s ur teɣri ara, maca d tin yesnen aṭas tamedyazt d Ccna aqbayli. Ikecm s-aɣerbaz alemmas deg [[Ṣṭif]] anida yedder iwala ayen iḍran ussan n mayu 1945.

Asegwas 1957 yemmugred amaru [[Lmulud Mɛemri|Mouloud At Mammar]], ig uɣalen d-amdakel-is ameqṛan. Iɛedda seg IDHEC (''Institut des hautes des Etudes Cinématographiques'') deg usegwas 1960; Bugermuḥ isker tidwilin i Tiliẓri RTF di ''Cognac Jay''.

Asegwas 1963 yuɣal-ed ɣer tmurt iwakken ad ittekki deg usnulfu n CNCA ''(Centre National Cinématographique Algérien)'', win seg anda tessufɣen deg 1964 ɣef tiktiwin ines. Asegwas 1965 seg uḍris n Malek Ḥeddad issufɣed ''(comme une âme)'' asaru s tmaziɣt, asaru agi ur yettwaqbel ara seg uɣlif adzayri it yebɣan s taɛrabt; Sinna yunag ɣer [[Paris|lpari]] yessufɣed asaru s tefṛansist, ayagi dayen is-d yewwin astixer i tikelt tisnat, d-huddu n-asaru. asrau yagi werǧin id yeffaɣ ar assa.

Seg 1965 armi 1968 isker-ed amazrar n imselɣet yarna yewwid tamusni d imusnawen iqedcen ɣef timmuzɣa, garasen mass Ḥannuz, [[Ṭawes Amṛuc]], [[Lmulud Mɛemri|Mulud At Mammar]], [[Mulud Baṭuc]], [[Beṣawud Muḥand Aṛab]]. Amseḍru yarra ddahn-is ɣer yiwen imselɣet (usaru) aɣermiw, sinna isker-ed asaru ''la grive'' asegwas 1967. Asaru id yewwin aṭas n warazen, yarna d win yellan ɣur ineɣmasen d-amenzu deg usarag Adzayri.

Asegwas 1968, issars ''La coline oubliée Tawrirt yettwattun'' anda yura dakken asaru yagi ur yezmir ad yettwaxdem ala s teqbaylit, maca asenfaṛ agi arrant-id (ugin-t) mebla asegzi. Ayagi yeǧǧat ad yidir isegwasen mebla leqdic, armi d-asegwas 1973 anida id isker d Mohamed Lakhdar Hamina deg ''Chronique des années de braises''.

Issufɣed (isker-ed) i Tiliẓri wa deffir wayeḍ ''les oiseaux de l'été'', asegwas 1978 d ''Kahla oua beida'', asegwas 1980, id yemmugren tarennawet tameqṛant. asegwas 1987, isker asaru ines ameqṛan 35mm ''Cri de pierre'', id yewwin aṭas n warazen barra n tmurt, maca di ldzayer wten-d deg-s. Deg usegwas 1989 yewwid ttriḥ iwakken ad yessuffeɣ s tmaziɣt (taqbaylit) [[Tawrirt yettwattun]] id yefɣen di 1996.

Seg isegwasen n 60' isker-ed aṭas isura imecṭaḥ, d wiɣaḍ imeqṛanen in Tiliẓri RTA ''Les Oiseaux de l'été'' (1978) d ''Noir et blanc'' (1986), ''Cri de pierre'' (1986), ''La Colline oubliée'' (1996).

